  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Cut the <strong>paneer </strong>in half widthways, then slice each half into 6 strips, so that you are left with 12 <span class=\"text-danger\">[24]</span> equal strips </span></p>\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>paneer</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min <span class=\"text-highlight\">or until golden, then transfer the<strong> paneer</strong> to a plate (reserve the pan) and cover with <strong>tin foil </strong></span></p>",
